&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction
  &lt;a href=&#34;#introduction&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;anchor-symbol&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; height=&#34;26&#34; width=&#34;26&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 22 22&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;
      &lt;path d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;
      &lt;path d=&#34;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76.0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71.0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71.0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76.0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;
    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I performed a 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://zenodo.org/record/1475795#.X-YrudgzYuE&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;study&lt;/a&gt; in 2018 to identify the core topics in 98 full-text library and information science Electronic Theses and Dissertations (ETDs) using 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://code.google.com/archive/p/topic-modeling-tool/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Topic-Modeling-Toolkit&lt;/a&gt; for the period of 2013-2017.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The dashboard helps to visualize the topic modeling results of the above study. It was prepared using 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tableau.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Tableau&lt;/a&gt; on 25 December 2020 and was updated on 13 June 2021. The data used to prepare the dashboard is available for download and can be searched using the publication year, topics, and keywords for title.&lt;/p&gt;
